item.title: CVE-2022-41267|2024-08-03T12:42:44.072Z -- sap -- businessobjects%20business%20intelligence%20platform
item.description: SAP Business Objects Platform - versions 420, and 430, allows an attacker with normal BI user privileges to upload/replace any file on Business Objects server at the operating system level, enabling the attacker to take full control of the system causing a high impact on confidentiality, integrity, and availability of the application.
